1
00:00:00,166 --> 00:00:04,958
Psychological torture was exhausting and constant

2
00:00:05,666 --> 00:00:08,916
We were kept in the disciplinary cell

3
00:00:09,208 --> 00:00:12,208
They told us, You will not live long. Repent to your Lord

4
00:00:12,583 --> 00:00:16,416
And said things like, Your days are
numbered. Don’t think of getting out at all

5
00:00:17,041 --> 00:00:19,166
There were also people

6
00:00:20,041 --> 00:00:23,750
Among the prisoners whom they dressed in yellow clothes

7
00:00:24,541 --> 00:00:26,500
Their execution outfit

8
00:00:27,083 --> 00:00:29,000
They shaved their hair and beards

9
00:00:29,250 --> 00:00:34,291
Reenacting the steps of execution preparation

10
00:00:34,708 --> 00:00:37,708
Assuming he was not Muslim and they had the right to kill him

11
00:00:37,875 --> 00:00:42,083
Which was sometimes more terrifying
and painful than physical torture
